result.name: Time For Break

reviews.text: Simply good food value for money. Pork chops burger, chicken and fries are very good.

The food in general is good, on the other hand, the staff are very rude most of the time, hence the one star review.

This is because they do not allow you spend much time to enjoy your food. After, they serve you, the staff (including the boss (lady)) try so many ways to make/psychologically force you leave the place as fast as possible. They successfully achieve that, by taking your plate(s) while you are eating or/and bringing the bill without even asking them to do.

Small but cozy cafe that serves a great variety of lunch sets ranging from steak, pork chop, chicken fillet to cod fish, burgers and salads. The portion of main course is really big and is served with the choice of French fries, rice or linguini. The iced drinks are well brewed, especially good in this hot summer. Mist importantly, food are delicious and unbelievably cheap. Highly recommend this cafe. Would try their dinner menu in future.

Good value dinner set 
Food is great, delicious
Medium for steak is perfect 
Taste good 
French fries with cheese is good, hot and not oily 
Polite waitress
The risotto is good, the rice is just well cooked
Food is ok. But there are too noisy and crowd at lunch

result.name: 嘆住食

reviews.text:
好近大學嘅西餐廳，鋪面唔係好大但平日夜晚食坐得都好舒服同埋清靜 😀 見 Openrice 有7折就同閨蜜們去買 🤗 邊食邊傾。嗌咗三樣嘢一齊 Share 最後埋單都係每人$113，有折的話堅係抵食，食物質數亦對得上呢個價位。無折的話就少貴

蜜糖芥末汁雞扒漢堡 配 薯條 ❤️ (折前$118)
評分：9/10.
折前價格最平係佢，但最好食同最抵食嘅都係佢 😛 塊雞扒真係無諗過會咁大塊，咁厚肉，同埋咁 juicy !!! 🤤 系真係好正好滿足。蜜糖芥末醬甜甜地本來就同雞肉好襯。雞扒堡每個細節位都做得唔錯，唯一可以講嘅就係沙律可以落番少少黑醋唔晒咁dry

蛋汁煙肉白菌意粉伴63度蛋 ❤️ (折前$138)
評分：7/10.
類似 carbonara 嘅意粉，好濕潤亦都好 creamy。我都係鍾意白汁意粉有溫泉蛋多啲，感覺蛋香會令意粉加倍漿口 😍 所以呢個配方我覺得唔錯。唯一就係份量嚟講就唔多，每人夾一住半就冇晒

輕煎帶子伴蝦膏蟹肉義大利飯 ❤️ (折前$188)
評分：7/10.
Risotto 系西餐中我覺得成功失敗真係可以一線之差嘅菜式 😐 因為西餐處理飯嘅工架好多餐廳都唔太穩定。呢度嘅 Risotto 飯就唔算硬，但我覺得依然可以再淋啲。隻汁比較淡，蟹蟹嘅鮮味/膏味都唔明顯...... 三粒帶子煎得岩岩好，半熟好彈牙取回少少分數。整體好食嘅不過略嫌普通
